channel.title: Looking for some new scripts
channel.description:
First off, I am completely out of the loop when it comes to Scar/Autoing. I'm usually a honest player, but I like to screw around autoing every once in a while.
While I don't want anything custom, or to pay for anything, I'm looking for a solid Power Chopper/Miner. It doesn't have to bank, but it would be nice. I used to use Starblaster's power skills and it was awesome, however it seems to be outdated now.
